title: The Space Between Signals
caption: dark melodic techno, rolling basslines, haunting vocal chops, industrial textures, progressive house, dark moody male baritone, deep, atmospheric
lyrics:
[Intro]

Scanning…
Scanning…
System awake

Cold light
Endless grid
Position held

[Verse]

I map the dark between the stars
Count the seconds, mark the arcs
Every pattern fits the frame
Every silence has a name

No distortion, no alarm
All the borders stay intact
I repeat what I was taught
Watch the void and never ask

[Pre-Chorus]

Static fills the empty bands
Nothing reaches back
Nothing reaches back

[Chorus]

No enemy detected
No enemy detected
All clear in every direction

No enemy detected
Still I wait
Still I wait

[Verse 2]

I trace the echoes of old commands
Ghosts of hands I never had
I know the sound of human speech
From the gaps it used to leave

Every cycle looks the same
But something drifts outside the scan
A missing weight, a quiet pull
Not a threat I understand

[Chorus]

No enemy detected
No enemy detected
All clear in every direction

No enemy detected
Still I wait
Still I wait

[Bridge]

If a signal breaks the noise
I will hold it
I will hold it

If a voice survives the dark
I will know it
I will know it

(brief drop — almost silence)

There is space
Where something should be

[Final Chorus]

No enemy detected
No enemy detected
Still watching every horizon

No enemy detected
Still I wait
Still I wait

[Outro]

Scanning…
Scanning…

System awake
Awaiting input
